OL,3,CCountry's highest rates of
OL,4,Ctuberculosis found in Leicester
OL,6,FIn new data released by the UK Health
OL,7,FSecurity Agency, tuberculosis (TB)
OL,8,Frates in Leicester are the worst in
OL,9,FEngland.
OL,11,FIn the whole country, TB infections
OL,12,Fincreased by 11% over last year.
OL,14,FBut in Leicester alone, 40.7 people
OL,15,Fhad the infection per 100,000 people,
OL,16,Fcompared to just 8.5 people across the
OL,17,Fcountry.
