OL,6,FDeborah Watson, who is a TB lead and
OL,7,Fconsultant in the East Midlands said:
OL,8,F"TB is curable and preventable, but
OL,9,Fthe disease remains a serious public
OL,10,Fhealth issue in England and is of
OL,11,Fconcern in areas with high or rising
OL,12,Frates of TB such as Leicester."
OL,14,F"If you have moved to England in the
OL,15,Flast five years from a country where
OL,16,FTB is more common, please be aware of
OL,17,Fthe symptoms of TB so you can get
OL,18,Ftested and treated through your GP
OL,19,Fsurgery."
