OL,6,F"Not every persistent cough, along
OL,7,Fwith a fever, is caused by flu or
OL,8,FCOVID-19. A cough that usually has
OL,9,Fmucus and lasts longer than 3 weeks
OL,10,Fcan be caused by a range of other
OL,11,Fissues, including TB. Please speak to
OL,12,Fyour GP if you think you could be at
OL,13,Frisk."
