OL,6,FTo detect people with latent TB
OL,7,Finfection, a testing and treatment
OL,8,Fprogramme is in place in higher
OL,9,Fincidence areas of England for new
OL,10,Farrivals from higher incidence
OL,11,Fcountries. There was a 98.4% rise in
OL,12,Fthe number of people tested through
OL,13,Fthe NHS England Latent TB Infection
OL,14,F(LTBI) programme in 2023 (34, 680
OL,15,Fpeople compared to 17,484 in 2022.
OL,16,F15.1% of people tested positive for
OL,17,FLTBI.
