OL,6,FTuberculosis continues to be
OL,7,Fassociated with deprivation and the
OL,8,Finfection is more common in large
OL,9,Furban areas. For those born in the UK,
OL,10,FTB is more common among those who
OL,11,Fexperience homelessness, drug and
OL,12,Falcohol dependence and have had
OL,13,Fcontact with the criminal justice
OL,14,Fsystem.
